OL,5, A Post Office investigator has rejected
OL,6, any personal responsibility in the case
OL,7, of a wrongly-convicted manager, telling
OL,8, an inquiry: "I was only doing my job." 
OL,10,FRobert Daily investigated Peter Holmes,
OL,11,Fwho managed a post office in Jesmond,  
OL,12,FNewcastle, when an audit said there was
OL,13,Fa #46,000 shortfall in his account.    
OL,15,FMr Holmes was convicted in 2010, but   
OL,16,Fthe Court of Appeal quashed it in 2021.
OL,18,FYet Mr Holmes never got to see his name
OL,19,Fbeing cleared, having died from a brain
OL,20,Ftumour aged 74 in 2015.                
